{{Infobox hill | name = Tashmoo Hill | photo = | photo_caption = | map = Massachusetts#USA | map_caption = Location of Tashmoo Hill in Massachusetts | elevation_ft = 118 | elevation_ref = | location = [[Marthas Vineyard]], [[Massachusetts]] | range = | coordinates = {{coord|41.4459454|-70.6175284|region:US|format=dms}}<ref name="gnis">{{cite gnis | id = 606423 | name = Tashmoo Hill | accessdate = 2018-08-20}}</ref> | topo = [[United States Geological Survey|USGS]] ''Vineyard Haven'' | first_ascent = | easiest_route = }}
'''Tashmoo Hill''' is a [[hill]] in [[Dukes County, Massachusetts]]. It is located on [[Marthas Vineyard]] southwest of [[Vineyard Haven, Massachusetts|Vineyard Haven]] in the [[Tisbury, Massachusetts|Town of Tisbury]]. [[Pilot Hill (Massachusetts)|Pilot Hill]] is located west-northwest of Tashmoo Hill.
